The program is designed to analyze the vocabulary of articles on websites, aiming to assist language learners in easier learning and acquiring high-frequency words.
本程序用於分析網站內文章的詞彙，用於幫助語言學習者更容易學習和獲取高頻詞彙。

Currently, three functions have been developed. They are to count the occurrences of specified words in the articles, to identify words that appear a certain number of times, and to list high-frequency words.
目前已經開發三個功能。分別是統計指定詞彙在文章出現次數，出現一定次數的詞彙，列出高頻詞彙。

You can choose to filter out common words that are not necessary for deliberate learning.
你可以選擇過濾掉常見且不需要刻意學習的詞彙。

Below is the list of filtered words. You can choose to delete or add new words as needed.
下面是過濾詞彙列表，你可以選擇自行刪除或者添加新詞彙
COMMON_WORDS = ["a", "the", "is", "and", "of", "to", "in", "that", "it", "for", "with", "as", "on", "at", "I", "you", "he", "she",
                "we", "they", "me", "him", "her", "us", "them", "this", "that", "these", "those", "here", "there", "when", "where",
                "why", "how", "which", "what", "who", "whom", "whose", "if", "then", "else", "not", "be", "have", "do", "can", "will",
                "would", "could", "should", "might", "must",]

Before using it, you need to install two libraries in advance.
使用前你需要預先安裝一些庫

pip install requests

pip install beautifulsoup4

In the IDE, open the terminal, input the specified command, press Enter, and wait for the installation to complete\
在IDE打開終端輸入指定，按回車鍵，等待安裝完成即可
